519138014, \"rank\": 0.0009485715601456307, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 375, \"end\": 387, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 25-year-old star has been cleared to compete in the women's event amid a gender eligibility row, with Khelief previously disqualified from the Women's World Boxing Championships last year.\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 582, \"end\": 588, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7316505392189096e-15, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif had been kicked out after her elevated levels of testosterone failed to meet the eligibility criteria.The Algerian Olympic Committee, for their part, hit back by saying her elimination was part of a 'conspiracy' to stop them from winning a gold medal.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 873, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Algerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also said her high testosterone levels were down to 'medical reasons'.Olympics fans have raged after Imane Khelif beat Angela Carini in the boxing on Thursday|GETTYOn Thursday, Khelif took the ring for the first time at the Olympics.She beat Italian s