 she could 'only adapt to the rules of the Olympics'.The International Boxing Association released a statement on Wednesday expressing concerns over allow Khelif to compete, however.\", \"from\": 2022, \"to\": 2242, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2023, \"end\": 2029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9958080185330894, \"rank\": 0.004209628150317891, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 2117, \"end\": 2149, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.310845272005344e-26, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As stated, the International Boxing Association (IBA) feels it appropriate at this prevalent time, to address recent media statements regarding those athletes Lin Yu-ting and Imane Khelif, particularly regarding their participation in the Paris Olympic Games 2024,\\\" they said.LATEST SPORTS NEWS:Rafael Nadal delivers alarming statement after being dumped out of Olympics doubles with Carlos AlcarazOlympics athletes 'think there is a huge issue brewing in Paris' after Adam Peaty's positive Covid testEngland next manager: Jurgen Klopp does not hold back after Gareth Southgate exit - 'Must have missed that'Olympics star Imane Khelif beat Angela Carini within just 46 seconds on Thursday|GETTY\\\"We wish to make the following points in these regards:\\\"On 24 March 2023, IBA disqualified athletes Lin Yu-ting and Imane Khelif from the IBA Women's World Boxing Championships New Delhi 2023.\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2258, \"end\": 2290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/