roadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 3037, \"end\": 3048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lin Yu-ting\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lin_Yu-ting\"}, {\"begin\": 3053, \"end\": 3065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 3075, \"end\": 3078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 3093, \"end\": 3099, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7316505392189096e-15, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 3114, \"end\": 3123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.998366669133119, \"rank\": 0.0016360029332502248, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This disqualification was a result of their failure to meet the eligibility criteria for participating in the women's competition, as set and laid out in the IBA Regulations.\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3304, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision, made after a meticulous review, was extremely important and necessary to uphold the level of fairness and utmost integrity of the competition.\", \"from\": 3305, \"to\": 3462, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Point to note, the athletes did not undergo a testosterone examination but were subject to a separate and recognised test, whereby the specifics remain confidential.\", \"from\": 3462, \"to\": 3628, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This test conclusively indicated that both athletes did not meet the required necessary eligibility criteria and were found to have competitive advantages over other female competitors.Olympics star Angela Carini was devastated after her defeat on Thursday|GETTY\\\"The decision made by IBA on 24 March 2023, was subsequently ratified by the IBA Board of Directors on 25 March 2023.\", \"from\": 3628, \"to\": 4008, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3828, \"end\": 3841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 3913, \"end\": 3916, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The official record of this decision can be accessed on the IBA website here IBA Board of Directors Meeting Minutes.\", \"from\": 4009, \"to\": 4125, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4069, \"end\": 4072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They also said: \\\"Our Committees have rigorously reviewed and endorsed the decision made during the World Championships.\", \"from\": 4125, \"to\": 4245, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While IBA remains committed to ensuring competitive fairness in all of our events, we express concern over the inconsistent application of eligibility criteria by other sporting organizations, including those overseeing the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 4245, \"to\": 4484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4252, \"end\": 4255, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The IOC's differing regulations on these matters, in which IBA is not involved, raise serious questions about both competitive fairness and athletes' safety.\", \"from\": 4484, \"to\": 4642, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4489, \"end\": 4492, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3976146153070019e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4544, \"end\": 4547, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For clarification on why the IOC permits athletes with competitive advantages to compete in their events, we urge interested parties to seek answers directly from the IOC.\\\"\", \"from\": 4642, \"to\": 4815, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4672, \"end\": 4675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3976146153070019e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 4810, \"end\": 4813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3976146153070019e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Khelif had been kicked out after her elevated levels of testosterone failed to meet the eligibility criteria.\", \"from\": 4817, \"to\": 4926, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian Olympic Committee, for their part, hit back by saying her elimination was part of a 'conspiracy' to stop them from winning a gold medal.\", \"from\": 4928, \"to\": 5077, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4932, \"end\": 4958, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Algerian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algerian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also said her high testosterone levels were down to 'medical reasons'.\", \"from\": 5078, \"to\": 5153, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics fans have raged after Imane Khelif beat Angela Carini in the boxing on Thursday  GETTY  On Thursday, Khelif took the ring for the first time at the Olympics.\", \"from\": 5155, \"to\": 5321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5186, \"end\": 5198, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 5204, \"end\": 5217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She beat Italian star Angela Carini, who withdrew after just 46 seconds following two early punches in the opening round.\", \"from\": 5323, \"to\": 5444, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5332, \"end\": 5339, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"score\": 0.8729338554198328, \"rank\": 0.14269416215691993, \"text\": \"Italian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 5345, \"end\": 5358, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Carini was visibly emotional after her defeat, with the 25-year-old crying inside the ring.\", \"from\": 5446, \"to\": 5537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5446, \"end\": 5452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"score\": 0.9958080185330894, \"rank\": 0.004209628150317891, \"text\": \"Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And fans on X are not happy with Khelif winning, with one user saying: \\\"The end of equality in sport.\", \"from\": 5539, \"to\": 5640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Shame on the IOC.\\\"\", \"from\": 5641, \"to\": 5659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5654, \"end\": 5657, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3976146153070019e-29, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"JUST IN:Mike Tyson receives 'catastrophic' message ahead of boxing fight with Jake Paul  A second said: \\\"@iocmedia why do you guys allow this in the sport?\\\"\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5817, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5669, \"end\": 5679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.686542607825755e-41, \"text\": \"Mike Tyson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mike_Tyson\"}, {\"begin\": 5739, \"end\": 5748, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jake Paul\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jake_Paul\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A third stated: \\\"This is a scandal!\", \"from\": 5819, \"to\": 5854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am done with this Olympic Spirit.\", \"from\": 5855, \"to\": 5890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5875, \"end\": 5889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Spirit\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Olympic Spirit\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Spirit\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Spirit\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I feel so sorry for Angela Carini.\\\"\", \"from\": 5891, \"to\": 5926, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5911, \"end\": 5924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another said: \\\"Absolute disgrace to put her in that position.\\\"\", \"from\": 5928, \"to\": 5990, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A fifth weighed in by saying: \\\"This is outrageous and disgraceful.\\\"\", \"from\": 5992, \"to\": 6059, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"READ MORE:Tom Daley makes complaint about Olympic Village as diving star talks Andy Murray and Rafael Nadal encounters  And a sixth raged: \\\"Complete outrage.\", \"from\": 6061, \"to\": 6218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6071, \"end\": 6080, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5815591169561836e-37, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}, {\"begin\": 6103, \"end\": 6118, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 6.524538990262921e-13, \"text\": \"Olympic Village\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Village\"}, {\"begin\": 6140, \"end\": 6151, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.715654903502736e-36, \"text\": \"Andy Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\",