d\": 7009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}, {\"begin\": 7024, \"end\": 7030, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.7316505392189096e-15, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}, {\"begin\": 7045, \"end\": 7054, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.998366669133119, \"rank\": 0.0016360029332502248, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This disqualification was a result of their failure to meet the eligibility criteria for participating in the women's competition, as set and laid out in the IBA Regulations.\", \"from\": 7061, \"to\": 7235, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This decision, made after a meticulous review, was extremely important and necessary to uphold the level of fairness and utmost integrity of the competition.\", \"from\": 7236, \"to\": 7393, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Point to note, the athletes did not undergo a testosterone examination but were subject to a separate and recognised test, whereby the specifics remain confidential.\", \"from\": 7395, \"to\": 7561, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This test conclusively indicated that both athletes did not meet the required necessary eligibility criteria and were found to have competitive advantages over other female competitors.\", \"from\": 7563, \"to\": 7749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympics star Angela Carini was devastated after her defeat on Thursday  GETTY  \\\"The decision made by IBA on 24 March 2023, was subsequently ratified by the IBA Board of Directors on 25 March 2023.\", \"from\": 7751, \"to\": 7948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7765, \"end\": 7778, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}, {\"begin\": 7853, \"end\": 7856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The official record of this decision can be accessed on the IBA website here IBA Board of Directors Meeting Minutes.\\\"\", \"from\": 7949, \"to\": 8066, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8009, \"end\": 8012, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9999999994088284, \"rank\": 5.899878292486825e-10, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They also said: \\\"Our Committees have rigorously reviewed and endorsed the decision made during the World Championships.\", \"from\": 8068, \"to\": 8187, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While IBA remains committed to ensuring competitive fairness in all of our events, we express concern over the inconsistent application of eligibility criteria by other sporting organizations, including those overseeing the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 8189, \"to\": 8428, \"en